Accompanying development for: ``Stop When you are Almost-Full'' paper
=====================================================================

To build:
~~~~~~~~~
   Edit Makefile to add the right path to coqc and type 'make'

Individual files:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  AlmostFull.v          -- Basic setup, connections to well-founded relations
  AFConstructions.v     -- AF relation constructions and type-based combinators
  AlmostFullInduction.v -- Various induction principles 
  AFExamples.v          -- Examples
  Terminator.v          -- Deriving the Terminator proof rule


